Text: Thanks.  This has been around before at low quality, this is much better!

At first I thought It was a mistake - the mistake being that neither THE BEATLES or THE STONES were on the cover, but then I Downloaded it and realized that these assholes left out 98% of the greatest songs of the 60s. Where are the Kinks, the stones, the who? Anyway, I'm not complaining just voicing my opinion. THANKS A MILL NEON
Also missing "The Mammas and the Pappas".
